      ```
      
  - Required Coverage Configuration:
      - All test projects MUST include coverage collection
      - Minimum threshold of 80% for line, branch, and method coverage
      - Buildingblocks are temporarily excluded from coverage requirements
      - Use ExcludeByFile to exclude buildingblocks: `**/buildingblocks/**/*.cs`
      - Coverage reports should be generated in cobertura format for CI/CD integration

